{"tid":1602429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【科技台】Musk更新Starship相關資訊，最快兩個月內 MK1就能首飛","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:01:06.000Z","uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd72ba24499a25298c8251588a61d8b4d32e618f","tid":1602429,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/09/29/musk-starship-mk1-update/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2019%2F09%2F29%2Fmusk-starship-mk1-update%2F&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLcQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=9816b692\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/09/29/musk-starship-mk1-update/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2Fb4db71a0-e267-11e9-9bf9-31903e9abc2f&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=f98071bf1a3c8a2301c3d0c4309e07d89546bec0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252Fb4db71a0-e267-11e9-9bf9-31903e9abc2f%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3Df98071bf1a3c8a2301c3d0c4309e07d89546bec0&h=e3a94036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一如預告的，Elon Musk 今早在 Boca Chica（當地時間是週六晚上）舉辦了 Starship 最新設計的說明會。原來這日期的選定不是個意外，而是特意選擇了 Falcon 1 火箭的第四次（也是終於成功的那一次）發射 11 週年的日子。在現場 SpaceX 還特地放了一支 Falcon 1 在一旁做為比較呢。<br />\n<br />\n「2019 年版」的 Starship 基本上除了翼面配置上的變化，以及機身變成閃亮亮的金屬之外，其實基本大小已經差不多定形，保持著 50m 長、9m 直徑的大小，空重為 120 公噸（投影片有誤），目標是能將 150 公噸重的酬載送入低地軌道。它將配備 6 具 Raptor 引擎，在中間的三個為海平面／真空兩用，而外圍的三個則是針對真空進行最佳化。SpaceX 顯然是放棄（或說不需要）靠著「流汗」來協助抵抗回返大氣的高熱，換成了可重複利用的隔熱瓷磚貼在底部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2Fb2ba49e0-e268-11e9-8731-8ad8198343ab&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=cbd31b2192e450a3d646bd2c6d19e42bed06907a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252Fb2ba49e0-e268-11e9-8731-8ad8198343ab%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3Dcbd31b2192e450a3d646bd2c6d19e42bed06907a&h=119fc47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Super Heavy 推進器的部份，長度維持著 68m，也就是說 Starship 的全長將來到 118m。它將配備 37 具 Raptor 引擎，不過由於目前 SpaceX 的開發重心將先放在 Starship 上，關於 Super Heavy 的更多資訊可能還要等未來再公開了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2Fd402cbe0-e268-11e9-bfff-5909ba1b7026&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=836330d62cace2bce1b43ebf0599e8cf1f9fc350\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252Fd402cbe0-e268-11e9-bfff-5909ba1b7026%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D836330d62cace2bce1b43ebf0599e8cf1f9fc350&h=ae5c046c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場展示的 Starship MK1 主要會以測試新的空氣動力設計為主，依 Musk 的推估，在未來「一兩個月內」就會發射到 20 公里的高度，再落回地面著陸。Starship 的著陸方式相當奇特，依 Musk 的形容它像是高空跳傘一樣，會以「肚皮朝下」的姿勢下落，靠著四片控制翼面保持平衡，直到最後一刻才用小的儀態控制火箭「轉正」，變成尾巴朝下的姿勢減速落地。由於這種著陸方式還沒有任何人嘗試過，因此測試還是要一步一步來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F1f7f4a30-e269-11e9-bbc6-8918a2f923e2&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=236d540982e1f17d5b1b7a6a28a2e788b5fd07fa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252F1f7f4a30-e269-11e9-bbc6-8918a2f923e2%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D236d540982e1f17d5b1b7a6a28a2e788b5fd07fa&h=dea40992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMusk 表示 Starship 的設計和建造方式都在高速改進當中，雖然目前同步建造當中的德州 Starship MK1 與佛州 Starship MK2 都是將不鏽做成「環」，再將一圈一圈的環堆疊起來，但接下來的新 Starhip 會用螺旋的方式將一長條的不鏽鋼「卷」成圓柱，這可望大幅加速 Starship 的生產。MK3 和 MK4 分別可能最快 3~5 個月內就能完工，而如果大氣內的測試順利的話，MK4 或 MK5 就有機會在六個月內首度入軌。當然，這個時程要考慮到 Musk 通常過度樂觀的預估和 Raptor 引擎的產量，但我們應該有很大的機會至少在明年內看到 Starship 的首度入軌吧？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F5b8754f0-e269-11e9-96fe-86c9fa9c73db&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=4e89b87c42e587a516bcc13b786feb1568f263d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252F5b8754f0-e269-11e9-96fe-86c9fa9c73db%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D4e89b87c42e587a516bcc13b786feb1568f263d1&h=e44d7ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再往後就很難說了。Musk 想要在明年底前就首度讓 Starship 載人，但這前提是要非常緊密的測試時程，也要考慮到美國政府會不會插手安全性相關的規範。總之還是先別想這麼遠，先來期待 MK1 的首飛吧！"},{"pid":"050304c0949711d132f06ccc44b746e232e09454","tid":1602429,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"a3e2cb1b52417aabb946946e7d68be4792d076c8","tid":1602429,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e8fcdb22d76b6f7ac27abaaf77c007226cf50e","tid":1602429,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}